  <brief_title>A Randomized Study to Establish the Efficacy of Oral Ice Exposure During Oxaliplatin Infusion in Preventing Oral Cold Sensitivity</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Study to Establish the Efficacy of Oral Ice Exposure During Oxaliplatin Infusion in Preventing Oral Cold Sensitivity</official_title>
