  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main purpose of this study is to evaluate whether exposure to ice chips in the mouth
      (oral ice chips) during oxaliplatin treatment prevents or reduces symptoms of cold
      sensitivity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
